[ thunder booming ]

47:18.705 --> 47:22.404
[ Claire sighs ]

47:22.535 --> 47:23.928
Christ.

47:26.191 --> 47:28.715
Ye're a brave wee thing.

47:28.846 --> 47:30.673
[ chuckles ]

47:33.241 --> 47:34.852
Am I?

47:37.985 --> 47:39.247
Aye.

47:47.038 --> 47:48.648
How do you feel?

47:54.828 --> 47:55.916
Safe.

47:58.266 --> 48:00.965
[ thunder rumbling ]

48:02.444 --> 48:05.230
[ inhales deeply,
